  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Location_map_Known_world.svg\" class=\"image\" title=\"Leng Ma is located in The Known World\"><img alt=\"Leng Ma is located in The Known World\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/69/Location_map_Known_world.svg/400px-Location_map_Known_world.svg.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"267\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/69/Location_map_Known_world.svg/600px-Location_map_Known_world.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/69/Location_map_Known_world.svg/800px-Location_map_Known_world.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 81.7%; left: 86.2%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Leng Ma\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; top:-2.65em; left:-3em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Leng Ma</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">Location of Leng Ma in the <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Leng Ma</b> is a city on the island <a href=\"/index.php/Leng\" title=\"Leng\">Leng</a> in the eastern <a href=\"/index.php/Jade_Sea\" title=\"Jade Sea\">Jade Sea</a>. It is located on the western shore of the forested island, near the mouth of a river.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n<